OL,15, Bandai's Attempt to enter the second   
OL,16, generation.  This 8 bit Z80 based      
OL,17, computer lacked a built-in OS and      
OL,18, needed a cartridge to do anything.     
OL,20, The Basic cartridge also included the  
OL,21, Ear and Mic ports needed to save and   
OL,22, load from tape.                        
